{"tid":1496814,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要同政府鬥長命","createTime":"2019-08-22T16:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T19:06:14.000Z","uid":272925,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fed4829d76497aac8a2d2128a8ee995582413ba0","tid":1496814,"uid":272925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:30:44.000Z","msg":"今時今日大集團已沒有中立的自由，可以從國泰，匯豐連日黎的情況看到，現在開始清算，之後有機會金融業界，教育界借教育改革搵老師開刀，傳媒更加自我審查，公務員團隊，黎緊區議會參選人政府繼續用佢地facebook言論去DQ，最後可能醫務團隊，香港人我地去到退無可退，兄弟爬山，互相合作，不要即時勝利目光，要有持久戰的準備。抗爭要多元化，遊行，靜坐，抗爭音樂會，警察暴力攝影展，海外報紙賣廣告，民間記者會，勇武前線不合作運動等等&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;務求同政府鬥長命，五大訴求，缺一不可。五大訴求係最基本"},{"pid":"74f7a8084ced327d556744463c8d638f2dbc9c33","tid":1496814,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:32:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">是日（823星期五）活動<br />\n銀髮族罷買<br />\n會計界遊行<br />\n基督徒集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人鏈</span><br />\n賣港城一日遊</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BXTv9tG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBXTv9tG.png&h=e866629a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港，時代革命</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204bcfee2970c0ca86d1ee5e4eb510e21aab438d","tid":1496814,"uid":56328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T19:00:15.000Z","msg":"金融同會計界已經奶緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a6510e20e8e5c7982e42b49b5a82a34cbfe603","tid":1496814,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T19:06:14.000Z","msg":"其實而家中共改變左策略:<br />\n對付和理非一切既遊行, 罷工, 以致僅僅係社交媒體表態, 佢地洗人督佢地灰, 然後迫僱用佢地既企業施壓, 最後炒人. 同時係中港邊境度搞佢地.<br />\n對付勇武派行動, 而家係咁裝緊超多人面監控柱, 令義士再隱藏唔到身分, 可隨時逮補, 達致威嚇作用. 又迫狗鐵停駛, 斷後路."}]}